text.section:
The plan of operation shall, in addition to requirements enumerated elsewhere in this subtitle:
Establish procedures for handling the assets of the association;
Establish the amount and method of reimbursing members of the board of directors under KRS 304.42-070;
Establish regular places and times for meetings of the board of directors;
Establish procedures for records to be kept of all financial transactions of the association, its agents, and the board of directors;
Establish the procedures whereby selections for the board of directors will be made and submitted to the commissioner;
Establish any additional procedures for assessments under KRS 304.42-090;
Contain additional provisions necessary or proper for the execution of the powers and duties of the association.
